The Proposal: -
The Deputy Director of Health Services, vide the Government Decision No. 2 & 3 above,
G. Sambhajinagar Board, Health Institutions under G. Sambhajinagar
The temporary posts were extended till date 31.08.2024. This extension has expired.
Since these positions have arrived and are no longer needed, these positions will have to be filled by the date 01.09.2024.
An extension to the date 28.02.2025 was under consideration of the government.
The Government's Decisions:
Subordinate to Deputy Director, Health Services, G. Sambhajinagar Circle, G. Sambhajinagar
Provisional posts in existing health institutions. Extended until 31.08.2024
With the expiry of the said extension, the Commissionerate of Health Services has issued the aforesaid Reference No. 1 here.
In the letter, a proposal to extend these posts has been submitted to the government.
2. Mentioned in "Annexure-A" annexed to this Government Decision.
Health under Deputy Director, Health Services, G. Sambhajinagar Mandal, G. Sambhajinagar
Extension of Temporary Posts in Institutions from Date 01.09.2024 to Date 28.02.2025
It's coming.
3. The salaries of these temporary posts shall be expended in the next head of account and this expenditure shall be borne by the
2024-2025 to be subtracted from this year's approved grant.
4. The said Government Decision No. Post-2016 / Q. No. 8/16 of the Finance Department, dated
Issued in accordance with the powers conferred on administrative divisions by the Government Decision of 06.09.2024
is being done.
